Signature by Levi Strauss & Co.™ Men's Relaxed Fit are quality, modern jeans built strong enough to last. With a straight, fuller leg and all-around relaxed fit through the seat and thigh, these jeans are created with premium flex denim that moves with you throughout the day. Signature by Levi Strauss & Co.™ Men's Relaxed Fit Jeans are so relaxed, you don’t have to break them in.
